Yasmin Abdel Aziz (Yāsmīn ʿAbd Al-ʿAzīz; amụrụ na 16 Jenụwarị 1980) bụ onye Ijipt na-eme ihe nkiri.
Abdel Aziz malitere na mgbasa ozi mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na abụọ n'ihi otu n'ime ndị enyi nne ya nwere ụlọ ọrụ mgbasa ozi
Mgbe oge ụfọdụ gasịrị, ọ malitere ime ihe nkiri na telivishọn n'usoro nke akpọrọ A Woman From The Love Time nke bụ nnukwu ihe ịga nke ọma na gburugburu Middle East
Mgbe ihe ịga nke ọma a gasịrị, o mere obere usoro ọzọ a na-akpọ Kids Are Going Crazy

Abdel Aziz lekwasịrị anya n'oge ikpeazụ n'igosi ihe nkiri sinima karịa ihe nkiri telivishọn ebe ndị ọzọ na-eme ihe nkiri nke ọgbọ ya emeghị, ọ nwetakwara nnukwu ihe ịga nke ọma ya nke abụọ site n'ịpụta ya na onye na-eme egwuregwu na-atọ ọchị Ahmed Helmi na ihe nkiri ịhụnanya aha ya bụ Zaki-Chan, nke nwetara nnukwu mmeri na ụlọ ọrụ na izu mbụ ya.

N'afọ 2001, ya na Ashraf Abdel Baqi mere ihe nkiri akpọrọ Rasha Gareea na nke ọzọ n'afọ 2005 ya na Mostafa Qamar akpọrọ Hareem Karim, nke na-ekwu maka nwanyị nwere obi mgbawa nke chere na di ya ghọgburu ya mgbe ọ na-emeghị ya ka ọ gbalịa ịgwa ya eziokwu site n'ịkpọ kọleji ya
O mekwara nkiri dị egwu dị ka Farhan Molazem Adam na Qalb Gariee.
Onye na-eme ihe nkiri ahụ lụrụ onye ọchụnta ego Ijipt bụ Mohamed Nabil Halawa n'afọ 2001, ha nwere ụmụ abụọ, Yasmin na Seif-eldin, mana di na nwunye ahụ gbara alụkwaghịm n'afọ 2018

N'afọ 2020, onye na-eme ihe nkiri ahụ kpaliri ndị mgbasa ozi akụkọ banyere mmekọrịta ya na onye Egypt bụbu onye na-agba bọọlụ aka na onye na-ememe ihe nkiri Ahmed El-Awady, onye ọ lụrụ na Disemba 2019.
